Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{（コナン）\N新幹線…}The Shinkansen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{我が国が世界に誇る→\N}Our country's pride of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:09.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{最も安全な高速鉄道。\N}the safest express railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{その新幹線に何者かが→\N}Onto this Shinkansen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:14.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{爆弾をつめた\Nアタッシュケースを持ち込んだ。\N}someone brought an attaché case containing a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:19.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}{果たして　その爆弾は\Nいったいどこに！？\N}So then, just where is this bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:22.58,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A canvas stained black with crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.79,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}With brilliant detective skills, its color is changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.29,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}{＜黒いカバンの奇妙な乗客\N}A suspicious rider with a black suitcase!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.26,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}{タイムリミット　探偵団！＞}Time's running out, Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:31.03,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.95,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:35.97,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
