Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody shaves in the bullet train
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:32.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on the way to their best friend's wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:37.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I overslept 'cuz I was up late last night discussing things with a client!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:41.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please. You got drunk and fell asleep in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:42.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:46.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you along 'cuz you wanted to come, but I dunno why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:49.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the wedding's in Kyoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really wanted to go there too, didn't you, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we have to bring him along anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:58.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know we can't leave him all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are those new shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Dr. Agasa gave them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.95,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I made you something I'm sure you'll like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.41,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Power Kick Shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.80,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Kick a ball with these shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.38,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and the criminals won't know what hit them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.66,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It uses electricity and magnetic fields\Nto stimulate your feet muscles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.84,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}thereby substantially increasing your kick power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.46,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What about my glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:21.68,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They're ready too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.14,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I added a miniature hidden microphone to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.78,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm certain it'll come in handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I hope they actually work when I need them to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are they with us too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter?\NTheir tickets have been paid for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, parents these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Let's go exploring!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:50.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it'll be really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:51.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:57.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Their parents obviously have some issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about his parents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't even called us once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I gotta go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's not like I'm living with you because I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's all their fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They were the ones who forced me to take that weird pill
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and wind up small like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:34.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is my best chance to steal some of those pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Once I turn back into high school detective Shin'ichi Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll expose all of your evil deeds to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:41.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But what in the world could they be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They're meeting with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now's my chance to plant\NDr. Agasa's hidden microphone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}on one of their seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What are you doing, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:34.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't doing anything—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:35.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a troublemaker, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:46.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's people like you who give kids a bad name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should wrap the gum in paper and put it in an ashtray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:51.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll hear them just fine if it's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Learn from your friends, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:58.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all such good children!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:07.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I know you, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0},\Nthat wasn't any ordinary prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that gum some sort of secret weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those two men spies?! Hit men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:16.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be great if they were,\Nbut I was just being a troublemaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:25.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bore. Let's get back to exploring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for being a bore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:41.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:47.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's not them! They're not the men in black!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:52.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I got the wrong people! I feel like such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He has a suitcase instead of the attaché case he had before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Something's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The two suitcases are too different
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}for someone to accidentally mistake one for the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:21.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it! I'll use the doc's hidden microphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He said that if I turn the dial\Nto match the frequency,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}special sound waves will stimulate my eardrums,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}allowing me to hear with my glasses on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.74,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I can finally have a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I can hear them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This sure turned out to be an easy transaction, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.08,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:47.07,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't worry, nobody's listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:51.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But 100 million just for handing over that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world was inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Information about gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:59.49,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Information that's worth more than 100 million once it's put to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Probably's already sitting back down, smiling with glee
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and looking out at the last scenic view that the fool will ever get to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last scenic view?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Included inside the black case we handed over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:16.56,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...was a bomb that'll detonate in 10 seconds after receiving a large shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.41,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So if they accidentally drop the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The information is too important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:30.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, the explosion is set for 3:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a time bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. But when the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:38.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll unknowingly press the detonation button themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:42.96,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}10 seconds later, the entire bullet train gets blasted into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Into pieces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, 8 times 8 equals?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,64!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean "Happa 64"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,8 times 8 is 64!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,8 times 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,72!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:07.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid kid had me scared there for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.99,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now arriving at Nagoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hurry! We're getting off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:24.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait! There's still something I want to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:35.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let go! Let go!\N- I can't let you out of my sight, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is bad! Without them on board—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:45.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait. The person they made the transaction with is still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, man! 40 minutes until it explodes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:54.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I have to find the person before then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:59.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But how?! There's hundreds of passengers onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he have gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:22.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Someone onboard has a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop the train at the next station
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and evacuate all the passengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This train's gonna be blown to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Don't be teasing grownups.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:38.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. It isn't nice to disregard him\Njust because he's a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:42.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second while I call Anpan Man for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:47.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No good! They don't believe me one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:52.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Is anything interesting going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us know if you find another case to solve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:58.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Are these the only guys who'll listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:02.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There are tons of black briefcases;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}checking them all would be impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it! Is my only option to look for the bomb alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Find a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Remember back to the beginning of their conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:21.11,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I can finally have a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The dining car isn't non-smoking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:29.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ah! The person they met doesn't like cigarette smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Meaning that person doesn't smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means the person's in a non-smoking car!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Let's see, how many non-smoking cars were on this train...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:41.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we solving a mystery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There have to be more clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.84,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}100 million just for handing over that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.25,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What in the world was inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.94,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Information about gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:57.00,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Probably's already sitting back down, smiling with glee
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.86,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looking out at the last scenic view that the fool will ever get to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Where on this train can you see scenic views from the windows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:04.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The 2-story Green Cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:09.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 3 Green Cars, right?\NWhich ones are non-smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:12.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the second floor of Car 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what's goin' on, but let's go anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:18.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's too dangerous for children—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:22.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Detective Boys! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:37.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who could have the black briefcase with the bomb in it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:41.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}One...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.07,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:52.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll have to check them each one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:02.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Stock trading and a gold Rolex!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's rakin' in the dough all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:06.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey! Can I play that game too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! There's a bunch of circles and rectangles on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're disrupting my work! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Big meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:19.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me play this black one!\NIt's a game too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Owie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, little boy? Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good view this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:38.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? The weather is clear today so you can see Mt. Fuji from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:40.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mt. Fuji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn! It's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:54.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shut up already! What part of\N"go away" don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:54.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:58.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did you go to the dining car?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:02.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought you looked like the person who was there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with some men dressed in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you must have the wrong person then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to the dining car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:12.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could go anywhere when I'm this busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:25.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you go to the dining car a little while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, did you go to the dining car a little while ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:33.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why yes I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:37.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I go,\NDisneyland is always fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:43.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This isn't working out. I'll come back to him later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Gold rims!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey! Did you go to the dining car—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's really none of my business, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:11.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's a napkin from the dining car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:14.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This guy's been there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:15.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:19.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, my paper airplane got stuck up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind if I get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where is it? I can't find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.45,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Included inside the black case we handed over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:41.75,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...was a bomb that'll detonate in 10 seconds after receiving a large shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:56.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you knock it off already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Underwear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You lousy kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:25.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! The rest of you too! Give it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}14 minutes until it explodes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But that's one person down! Only three to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who has the bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn those freaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.40,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's a time bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.13,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No. But when the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:52.36,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}they'll unknowingly press the detonation button themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:57.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That means the explosion's set off by the person's reaction to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:03.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The three people have a laptop, a cell phone, and a tape player!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No good! They're all suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm still missing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to sit here and behave yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to go to the bathroom—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just went.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to buy those on your way back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:30.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do like to get into trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no! 7 minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The only choice now is to explain everything
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:39.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and have all the passengers evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:42.08,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But nobody'll believe me because I'm a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:46.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's only one way to make her believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If I tell her that I'm actually Shin'ichi Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran would have to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:53.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Everyone would believe her if she told them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:18:00.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If the bomb explodes, Ran and I and all the other passengers are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Say, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:09.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's not "Ran", it's "Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to use name suffixes for older people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hiding something from you this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:24.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:28.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm neither Conan Edogawa\Nnor a grade school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we pass the ocean already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, while you were looking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But these seats face the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:41.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't have seen it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:42.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Facing the mountains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.89,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What a good view this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:49.10,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Isn't it? The weather is clear today so you can see Mt. Fuji from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm sure those seats faced the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It would be impossible to see Mt. Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:58.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Then where did she see Mt. Fuji from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The dining car!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not good! Only one minute left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.21,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Attention, passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:14.64,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}As using cellular phones may disturb other passengers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:19.73,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}we ask that you step onto the outside deck before using your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it! The cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:28.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0} says she'll buy us any yummy food we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll take an eel boxed lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a full course of French cuisine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:37.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's impossible to plan for someone to press a key or button
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:42.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}on a laptop or tape player at exactly 3:10!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:46.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's entirely possible to have a predetermined time or phone number!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:02.05,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}{\a6}10 seconds later, the entire bullet train gets blasted into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa. A detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:30.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:34.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What have you done this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:36.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a grade school student though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:42.32,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Afterward, the bullet train was stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.45,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and Inspector Megure and his men began their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:47.57,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Being late to the wedding was a problem in itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:51.06,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but things somehow came to an end\Nwithout anyone getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:55.11,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It turns out she bought inside information about the trading market
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:57.46,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}from the two men for 100 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:00.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Apparently she was supposed to call them on a specific phone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:03.32,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}at a specific time to find out\Nhow to open the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:07.94,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But the two planned from the start to get rid of her after getting the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:15.41,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They were caught and arrested by an emergency police inspection line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:19.37,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I really jumped to conclusions though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:23.42,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Where did the real men in black who shrunk me go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:26.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it! I'll never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:29.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll catch up to you someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:31.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:01.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Say, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}. What were you about to tell me that one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.68,0:23:03.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:07.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pretend you don't know!\NYou were serious when you said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:10.89,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm neither Conan Edogawa\Nnor a grade school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:11.32,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:13.96,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:16.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who are you actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:20.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:22.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A genius at getting into trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:13.68,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT TIME... "TURNING POINT ON A DRIVING DATE"
